NK039(ti)035:0: rnam sras kyi gzigs phyogs legs so //
NK039(ti)035:2: phyogs dus rgyal ba thabs mkhas pas //
NK039(ti)035:4: rin chen mang gi sprul pa gter gyi bdag /
NK039(ti)035:5: rin chen 'khril bzhi'i bsnyen mchod 'di gsal bya //
NK039(ti)035:6: rgyal po rnam thos sras kyi bsgrub pa la drug ste /
NK039(ti)035:8: dam tshig pa bskyed pa dang /
NK039(ti)035:9: de 'dra spyan drangs la bstim pa dang /
NK039(ti)035:11: smon lam 'dod gsol bya ba dang /
NK039(ti)035:12: bsnyen cing phrin las bcol ba'o //
NK039(ti)035:14: de yang bkra shis pa'i sa la /
NK039(ti)035:16: rin po ches spras bri ba'i dbus su /
NK039(ti)035:17: gtor ma ri rab bang rim gsum pa /
NK039(ti)035:21: rgyal srid sna bdun ma he /
NK039(ti)035:25: mngar gsum gyis brgyan pa bshams la /
NK039(ti)035:27: spos bsreg cing gnyis pa ni /
NK039(ti)035:28: de nyid mi dmigs pa'i ngang las /
NK039(ti)035:29: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK039(ti)035:30: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i gter gyi pho brang chen po'i dbus su /
NK039(ti)035:31: rin po che'i gter gyi bum pa /
NK039(ti)035:32: de'i steng du seng ge dkar mo g.yu'i ral pa
NK039(ti)035:33: can rin po che'i rgyan cha dang kha nas rin
NK039(ti)035:35: de'i thog tu b+heehsera po 'od du ba las /
NK039(ti)035:36: rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras /
NK039(ti)035:38: gser gyi ri la nyi ma shar ba 'dra ba /
NK039(ti)035:39: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum zhi ma khro /
NK039(ti)035:40: dbu skra ral pa yal la bcing shing lhag ma mar la grol bas /
NK039(ti)035:44: zhabs phyed drung du bzhugs pa /
NK039(ti)035:45: rin po che'i rgyan rnam pa sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)035:47: g.yon ne'u le rin po ches bkang zhing /
NK039(ti)035:48: kha nas dgos 'dod thams cad phyur ba /
NK039(ti)035:49: thugs ka nas b+hehsera po la /
NK039(ti)035:51: de'i phyogs bzhir btsun mo bzhi /
NK039(ti)035:54: de rgyab klu chen po brgyad /
NK039(ti)035:55: de rgyab gnod sbyin bye ba'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK039(ti)035:61: snye ma la sogs pa'i phyag mtshan sna tshogs bsnams pa /
NK039(ti)035:64: dngos grub ster ba'i tshul du bzhugs par bsam la /
NK039(ti)035:65: badz+ra sa ma ya dza dzah gsum pa ni /
NK039(ti)035:72: byang phyogs rin chen gzhal yas nas //
NK039(ti)035:73: rin chen gter gyi pho brang na //
NK039(ti)035:74: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK039(ti)035:75: bstan pa bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK039(ti)035:76: b+he las byung ba'i mgon po ni //
NK039(ti)035:77: dpal ldan rgyal chen rnam thos sras //
NK039(ti)035:78: sku mdog ser gsal gser gyi mdog /
NK039(ti)035:79: phyag g.yas ga dar rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NK039(ti)035:80: bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan dar bar mdzad //
NK039(ti)035:81: phyag g.yon gter gyi ne'u le 'dzin //
NK039(ti)035:82: kha nas rin chen rat+na phyur //
NK039(ti)035:83: bsgrub pa po la dngos grub ster //
NK039(ti)035:84: sku la rin chen rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK039(ti)035:86: seng ge'i khri la bzhugs su gsol //
NK039(ti)035:87: 'khor du gnod sbyin chen po brgyad //
NK039(ti)035:88: mthu chen klu'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK039(ti)035:89: gnod sbyin bye ba 'bum dang bcas //
NK039(ti)035:90: ma lus gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)035:91: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK039(ti)035:93: khyod la mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK039(ti)035:94: mdzes pa'i gzugs dang snyan pa'i sgra //
NK039(ti)035:95: zhim pa'i dri dang mngar ba'i ro //
NK039(ti)035:96: reg bya bde 'jam sna tshogs pa'i //
NK039(ti)035:97: lhun po lta bu'i gtor ma dang //
NK039(ti)035:98: dam rdzas sna tshogs bsags pa dang //
NK039(ti)035:99: rin chen sna tshogs 'bru sna tshogs //
NK039(ti)035:100: bkra shis rdzas brgyad 'dod yon lnga /
NK039(ti)035:101: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun dang //
NK039(ti)035:102: rin chen gter gyi bum pa dang //
NK039(ti)035:103: phyii nang lha mo bcu drug dang //
NK039(ti)035:104: 'phan gdug bla re ba dan dang /
NK039(ti)035:105: rgyal mtshan rol mo sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)035:106: rta dang ma he mdzes pa'i bya //
NK039(ti)035:107: rin thang che ba'i dkor nor dang //
NK039(ti)035:108: kan ta ka ri seng khrom sle tres dang //
NK039(ti)035:109: chu srin sder mo dbang po lag pa sogs //
NK039(ti)035:110: dkar gsum 'o ma'i rgya mtsho dang //
NK039(ti)035:111: mngar gsum sman gyi sdong po dang //
NK039(ti)035:113: dpal ldan rgyal chen rnam thos sras //
NK039(ti)035:114: gnod sbyin chen po brgyad dang bcas //
NK039(ti)035:115: mthu chen klu yi 'khor tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)035:117: dngos grub stsol phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)035:118: khyed kyi thugs dam bskang bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)035:120: khyed kyi thugs dam bskangs nas kyang //
NK039(ti)035:121: bdag cag rnal 'byor bsgrub pa po //
NK039(ti)035:122: 'di nas bzung ste byang chub bar //
NK039(ti)035:123: tshe rabs skye ba thams cad du //
NK039(ti)035:124: bsod nams ye shes 'byor ldan zhing //
NK039(ti)035:125: snyan dang grags pa khyab pa dang //
NK039(ti)035:127: bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub pa shog /
NK039(ti)035:128: skye dgu thams cad rab dga' zhing //
NK039(ti)035:129: kun kyang gus shing 'dun pa dang //
NK039(ti)035:130: yid dang mthun pa'i dbang byas shing //
NK039(ti)035:131: grags dang snyan pas khyab par mdzod //
NK039(ti)035:132: byang chub lam la gnod pa yi //
NK039(ti)035:133: mi dang mi ma yin pa rnams //
NK039(ti)035:134: drag po'i las kyi tshar chod la //
NK039(ti)035:135: bskrad cing ring par byed pa dang //
NK039(ti)035:136: yang yang mthu stobs phrog nas su //
NK039(ti)035:137: ma lus rdul du rlag par mdzod //
NK039(ti)035:138: mgon po khyod kyi thugs dam dus la bab bo
NK039(ti)035:139: sa ma y+aa gnod sbyin brgyad kyi thugs dam dus
NK039(ti)035:140: la bab bo sa ma y+aa mthu chen klu yi
NK039(ti)035:141: tshogs kyi thugs dam dus la bab bo sa ma
NK039(ti)035:142: y+aa da lta nyid nas dngos grub rtsol cig thugs
NK039(ti)035:143: dam dus la bab po sa ma y+aa bcol pa'i
NK039(ti)035:145: thugs dam dus la bab bo sa ma y+aa drug pa ni /
NK039(ti)035:146: rang gi sngags brjod pa tsam las 'od zer spros /
NK039(ti)035:147: rgyal po rnam thos sras 'khor bcas kyi zas nor chos gsum gyi dngos grub ster bar bsam la /
NK039(ti)035:148: b+he sha ma na y+ae s+w+aa h+aa /
NK039(ti)035:150: zhes ci rigs par bzla bsnyen thun 'jog khang /
NK039(ti)035:151: pho nya'i mgon po rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras //
NK039(ti)035:152: 'khor gnod sbyin nor lha'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams kyi /
NK039(ti)035:153: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma rgya chen po 'di bzhes la /
NK039(ti)035:154: 'gal rkyen bar chad thams cad sol la /
NK039(ti)035:156: bsam pa'i don thams cad chos bzhin du 'grub par mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)035:157: ces 'dod pa'i don la gsol gdab bo //
NK039(ti)035:158: bar skabs su bskang ba dang /
NK039(ti)035:159: tshogs dang me mchod ci ltar 'grub ltar bya'o //
NK039(ti)035:160: dgos 'dod kun 'byung rin chen 'khril ba zhi yi //
NK039(ti)035:161: gtor bsgrub bsnyen mchod 'dir bsdus bsod nams des //
NK039(ti)035:162: 'gro ba'i dbul 'phong sdug bsngal rab bsal te /
NK039(ti)035:163: 'byor ldan bla med byang chub thob par shog /
NK039(ti)035:164: 'gal rkyen rtsad chod bar chad zhi ba dang //
NK039(ti)035:165: mthun rkyen dpal dang grags dang skal ba bzang //
NK039(ti)035:166: thos 'dzin blo dang shes rab che ba dang //
NK039(ti)035:167: mthar thug bla med byang chub thob par shog /
NK039(ti)035:168: rin chen 'khril bzhi'i gtor bsgrub bsnyen mchod dgos 'dod
NK039(ti)035:169: kun 'byung zhes bya ba 'dis sems can thams cad
